1. Definitions

"Restricted User" means:
(a) any national, state, provincial, county, municipal, tribal, territorial, or
    other government body or instrumentality;
(b) any military branch, defense ministry, armed service, paramilitary unit,
    intelligence service, law-enforcement agency, prison authority, border or
    customs authority, or public-security body;
(c) any public university, public laboratory, or other public-sector entity;
(d) any government-owned, government-controlled, or military-controlled entity;
(e) any contractor, subcontractor, consultant, reseller, systems integrator,
    or other person or entity acting for, on behalf of, or in support of any of
    the foregoing.

"Large Commercial User" means any for-profit entity that, alone or together with
its affiliates, satisfies one or more of the following:
(a) more than 250 employees;
(b) more than USD $50,000,000 in annual gross revenue;
(c) publicly traded status;
(d) majority ownership or control by an entity described in (a), (b), or (c).

"Free-Tier User" means any person or entity that is neither a Restricted User nor
a Large Commercial User.

"Original Source" means the official Hashsite repository or the official
Hashsite website designated by the copyright holder.

